Question 4 – Grade Classification (Nested if-else)
Scenario:
80 and above : Grade A
60–79       : Grade B
50–59       : Grade C
Below 50    : Fail
marks=int(input("Enter your mark:"))
if marks >= 80:
    print("GRADE A")
elif marks >= 60:
    print("GRADE B")
elif marks >=50:
    print("GRADE C")
else:
    print("FAIL")
